MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 881

DECLARING A CERTAIN PARCEL OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN THE CITY OF BAIS, NEGROS ORIENTAL AS CIVIL RESERVATION FOR SOCIALIZED HOUSING PURPOSES

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources, and by virtue of the powers vested in me by Law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO , President of the Republic of the Philippines, do hereby declare as civil reservation for socialized housing purposes under the administration of the City Government of Bais, a certain parcel of land of the public domain situated in the City of Bais, Province of Negros Oriental, containing an area of ONE HUNDRED FIFTY SIX THOUSAND FIVE HUNDRED EIGHTY SEVEN (156,587) square meters, more or less, subject to private rights, if there be any and to actual survey, which parcel is more particularly described as follows:

Lot 734-E-2

“A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot No. 734-E-2, Portion of Lot 734, Cad-115), Bais Cadastre, Timberland), situated in the Barangay of Poblacion, City of Bais, Province of Negros Oriental, Island of Negros. Bounded on the SW., along line 1-2 by Lot 734-D portion of Lot 734 which is inside A & D; on the NW., SW., and SE., along lines 2-3-4-5 by Lot 63, Cad.-115, Bais Cadastre; on the SW., along lines 5-6-7-8 by Lot 734-C portion of Lot 734 which is inside A & D; along lines 8-9-10 by Lot 37, Cad.-115, Bais Cadastre; along Line 10-11 by Lot 734-B portion of Lot 734 which is inside A & D; along Line 11-12 by Lot 33; along Line 12-13 by Lot 32 both of Cad.-115, Bais Cadastre; along Line 13-14 by Lot 734-A portion of Lot 734 which is inside A & D; on the NW., along Lines 14-15-16 with Tavera Street by Lot 734-E-1 (Timberland) Fishpond; on the NE., and SE., along Lines 16-17-18-19-20-21-22-23- by Boundary parcel ‑1, Cad. ‑115, Bais Cadastre; on the SE., along Line 23-24 by Cad. ‑115, Bais Cadastre; on the SW., and SE., along Lines 24-25-26-27-1 by Lot 725, Cad. ‑115, Bais Cadastre. Beginning at a point marked “1” on plan being N 84 deg. 28′ E., 83.13 m. from BBM No. 1, Bais cadastre, Cad. ‑115, thence:

